snippet.title: Southern Illinois Worship Center
snippet.description:
Southern Illinois Worship Center isLocated at 124 Lou Ann Drive in Herrin, Illinois, we are a southern Illinois church. 
Situated just off route 148, we are easy to find and within a short drive of many surrounding communities.

Service Times

Sundays  9:00 a.m., 11:00 a.m., and 1:00 p.m.

Tuesdays 10:00 a.m.

Wednesdays 7:00 p.m.

We strive to provide worship opportunities for most schedules. We also offer live streaming of our 11:00 a.m. service on Sundays and post previous messages online for your convenience.
